      <item>
        <title>Error when opening URLs that don’t finish with ‘/‘</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[alejandro]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi Everyone,</p>
<p>I have found a possible bug in Frontity. I notice this bug in my project and to know if I was doing it wrong I have reviewed your demos and I have found the same problem.</p>
<p>I am using Mars theme but it also happens in Twenty Twenty</p>
<p>The problem occurs when you use an url that doesn’t finish with “/”</p>
<p>For example in the Frontity demo (<a href="https://twentytwenty.frontity.org" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://twentytwenty.frontity.org</a>)</p>
<p><strong>Good Url</strong> → <a href="https://twentytwenty.frontity.org/tag/japan/" class="inline-onebox" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Tag: Japan - Test Frontity Blog</a></p>
<p><code>  https://twentytwenty.frontity.org/tag/japan/</code></p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066" title="image2.png"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066_2_602x317.png" alt="image2.png" data-base62-sha1="qrnpsjH2X92nHdfQRi4Y1hTSnd4" width="602" height="317" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066_2_602x317.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066_2_903x475.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066_2_1204x634.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b950c8a9241a2c391af77bb3b9105abf2e10f066_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>All information is displayed correctly</p>
<p><strong>Bad url</strong> → <a href="https://twentytwenty.frontity.org/tag/japan" class="inline-onebox" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Tag: Japan - Test Frontity Blog</a></p>
<p><code>https://twentytwenty.frontity.org/tag/japan</code></p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389" title="image1.png"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389_2_550x270.png" alt="image1.png" data-base62-sha1="1wTyCuSe74IiDmk3MEk3NfLDhjj" width="550" height="270" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389_2_550x270.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389_2_825x405.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389_2_1100x540.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0aba2185384b56c4ca7bbda43a1d2a264711e389_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>It shows this errors:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Image doesn’t load.</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>We have this error in console.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a" title="image3.png"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a_2_553x221.png" alt="image3.png" data-base62-sha1="tjFQ3qARZNk8cGRlzGY7DGwq1IK" width="553" height="221" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a_2_553x221.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a_2_829x331.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cd7866ae434af6741e9cbe8149e5d3e028930e0a_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>In our project we have been able to appreciate that any javascript that has to be executed on the client is not done. No delayed <a href="http://console.log/" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Console.log</a>, useEffect or lazy javascript is working.</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Someone else has been able to see if they have the same error or have found some solution or<br>
workaround?</strong></p>
<p><strong>Thanks in advance! And good job with Frontity, we are loving it <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=9" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:"></strong></p>
          <p><a href="https://community.frontity.org/t/error-when-opening-urls-that-don-t-finish-with/4184/1">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
